description: Welcome to this spacious 850-square-foot two-bedroom, one-bathroom condo nestled in the heart of South Boston’s vibrant West Side. Featuring hardwood floors throughout, a sunlit living area, and generous-sized bedrooms, this home offers a comfortable layout with plenty of potential. Just off the kitchen enjoy the private deck,  and just up the internal stairs you find the private roof deck offering stunning city views—a perfect spot for morning coffee or evening relaxation. Conveniently located near public transportation, restaurants, shops, and the Seaport, this unit provides the best of city living with neighborhood charm. Whether you're an investor or a homeowner ready to add your personal touch, this West Side gem is full of potential! Don’t miss this opportunity -- vacant and easy to show.
